0001B3r 2               ; Addition
0001B3r 2               ; This Macro only supports Immediate/Zeropage/Absolute addressing.
0001B3r 2               ; Other addressing modes are not optimized for speed.
0001B3r 2               ; Other addressing usage: add a, {$00, x} / add a, {($00), y}
